  "title": "Temp Storekeeper – (CCK / Tengah / Bukit Batok) #HMS",
  "description": "<p><strong>📦 Temp Storekeeper – (CCK / Tengah / Bukit Batok)</strong><br />💰 <strong>$10.50/hr</strong><br />🕒 <strong>5.5 days | Staggered shifts</strong><br />📍 <strong>Non patient-facing, healthcare environment</strong></p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Packing of medications into ziplock bags</p></li><li><p>Topping up drug bins</p></li><li><p>Assisting inventory staff with receiving stock from vendors</p></li><li><p>De-blistering medicines and portioning tablets using tools</p></li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Mon–Fri:</strong> 7.5 hrs/day (between <strong>8:00am – 6:00pm</strong>, staggered)</p></li><li><p><strong>Sat:</strong> 8:00am – 2:00pm</p></li><li><p><strong>Total:</strong> 42 hrs/week</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Able to <strong>lift cartons up to 10–12kg</strong> (trolley provided)</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Able to commit <strong>minimum 3 months</strong> with good attendance</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with <strong>vaccinations & serology tests</strong></p><ul><li><p><em>Note: If candidate resigns within 1 month, immnisation & serology costs will not be covered</em></p></li></ul></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>Interested?</strong><br />Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
